Inside Sales Engineer (REG/201403/02/SG)
Job ID
EPM-00007108
Country
Singapore
State/Province
Singapore
City
Singapore
Publish Start Date
Mar 20 2014
Job Level
Experienced (Non-Manager)
|
Responsibilities:
Provide technical product application support for customers and distributors through the analysis of current and/or proposed control systems and the suitability of Tescom pressure control products for use in those systems.
Evaluate requests for product modification for the purpose of extending Tescom’s pressure control products to new applications or for the purpose of meeting a specific customer’s existing needs.
Conduct evaluation testing on product designs to determine conformance to the product definition and customer needs.
Assist the Sales department in planning and conduction field and internal training sessions for Tescom products.
Work with sales and customers to understand customer needs of solutions and work with Engineering to design panels or Electronic Regulators system solutions.
Requirements:
Degree in Engineering with 3 to 5 years direct application or related experience.
Preferably have working knowledge with the application of control system hardware including valves, regulators, filters, pressure and flow measurement instrumentation, process controllers and PC’s used in industrial application and hydraulic and pneumatic control system dynamics.